e like in Tokyo?  ](https://wisemeteo.com/en/country/japan/region/tokyo/city/tokyo/season/winter)\nWinter 2026-2027 will be mainly cool and Temperature will go down to 0 °C on 18th January and up to its maximum of 14 °C on 3rd December ... \n[ Read forecast ](https://wisemeteo.com/en/country/japan/region/tokyo/city/tokyo/season/winter)\n[Terms of use](https://wisemeteo.com/en/rules/terms) | [Privacy Policy](https://wisemeteo.com/en/rules/privacy) | [Cookies](https://wisemeteo.com/en/rules/cookie)\n© WISE AI 2026\nOur website uses [cookies](https://wisemeteo.com/en/rules/cookie/).\nOK\n"
